title: Mark Millar: Ultimate Avengers 1-18 (Book 1-3|2009-11|Empire+MM)
description:
Overview:
   
  <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ultimate_Comics:_Avengers" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ultimate_Comics:_Avengers</a>
   
   
   
Contains:
   
   Ultimate Avengers 01-06 - The Next Generation (2009-10) (Dgtl-1280) (Zone-Empire)
   
   Ultimate Avengers 07-12 - Crime and Punishment (2010) (Dgtl-HR) (MM-InnerDemons)
   
   Ultimate Avengers 13-18 - Blade versus The Avengers (2010-11) (Minutemen)
   
    ( The numbering on the covers is by books, as in "Ultimate Avengers 3 Issue 2", 
      while the numbers in the indicia are ongoing, as in "Ultimate Avengers No 14", 
      and some of the releases were originally named according to the former and 
      others according to the latter scheme.
      
      Rather than leaving the names as they were and letting date prefixes take care 
      of the ordering, I imposed a unified naming scheme here, namely the ongoing 
      numbers followed by the issue name, which in turn simply consists of the book 
      name followed by the book-internal numbering. Which just so happens to end up 
      agreeing very nicely with the pattern I used in several earlier torrents... )
